<p>The post <a href="https://liftoff.io/blog/hero-wars-live-events-gamerefinery/">How Nexters’ Hero Wars Stayed on Top with a Winning Events Strategy</a> appeared first on <a href="https://liftoff.io">Liftoff</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p class="is-style-body-md"><a href="https://app.gamerefinery.com/game/587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b/overview">Hero Wars</a> is a popular RPG game that launched in 2016 to steady success. Since 2019, Hero Wars has <strong>consistently held a top 100 grossing position on US iOS</strong>, a testament to its exceptional long-term success in the market.<br><br>As a mature mobile game, Hero Wars achieved its success through a dynamic and expanding live event strategy, continuous iteration on core features, and the introduction of diverse monetization events and strategic collaborations to keep players engaged and spending.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="669" src="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Performance-1024x669.png" alt="" class="wp-image-35047" srcset="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Performance-1024x669.png 1024w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Performance-300x196.png 300w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Performance-1536x1003.png 1536w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Performance-72x47.png 72w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Performance-900x588.png 900w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Performance-1128x737.png 1128w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Performance-564x368.png 564w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Performance-375x245.png 375w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Performance.png 1834w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p class="is-style-body-md">Although Hero Wars is technically a mature game, the developers have found a way to increase revenue and DAU over successive periods. For example, we can see a spike in DAU from August 2024 to June 2025, making it a game we can learn from.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="692" src="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Alliance-Fantasy-1024x692.png" alt="" class="wp-image-35048" style="width:1128px;height:auto" srcset="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Alliance-Fantasy-1024x692.png 1024w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Alliance-Fantasy-300x203.png 300w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Alliance-Fantasy-1536x1038.png 1536w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Alliance-Fantasy-72x49.png 72w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Alliance-Fantasy-900x608.png 900w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Alliance-Fantasy-1128x762.png 1128w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Alliance-Fantasy-564x381.png 564w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Alliance-Fantasy-375x253.png 375w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Alliance-Fantasy.png 1796w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<div style="height:61px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow">
<p class="is-style-body-md">“<em>GameRefinery’s Live Event Tracker has become a cornerstone of how we approach LiveOps and event design. Beyond just monitoring competitor activity, it’s enabled our teams to identify and implement event and competition formats that are highly relevant to our product—with a measurable positive impact on key product metrics. Thanks to this level of actionable insight, we’ve been able to align with emerging trends early, making sure we don’t miss out on critical market shifts. More importantly, the tool has been instrumental in helping us shape a long-term LiveOps strategy grounded in competitive data rather than assumptions.</em>”</p>



<p class="is-style-body-md">Aleksandr Sveikovskii<br>LiveOps Product Owner, Nexters</p>
</blockquote>



<div style="height:61px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading is-style-title-md">Hacking the Live Event Calendar for Growth</h2>



<p class="is-style-body-md">A key strategic initiative behind the success of Hero Wars is the expansion of its live event calendar.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="636" src="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Events-Per-Day-1024x636.png" alt="Hero Wars Events Per Day" class="wp-image-35045" srcset="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Events-Per-Day-1024x636.png 1024w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Events-Per-Day-300x186.png 300w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Events-Per-Day-72x45.png 72w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Events-Per-Day-900x559.png 900w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Events-Per-Day-1128x701.png 1128w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Events-Per-Day-564x350.png 564w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Events-Per-Day-375x233.png 375w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Events-Per-Day.png 1198w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p class="is-style-body-md">Looking closely, we see that the overall event calendar expanded across various categories, but the key driver of growth is a significant increase in monetization-focused events.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="632" src="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Monetization-Events-1024x632.png" alt="Hero Wars Monetization Events" class="wp-image-35046" srcset="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Monetization-Events-1024x632.png 1024w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Monetization-Events-300x185.png 300w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Monetization-Events-72x44.png 72w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Monetization-Events-900x555.png 900w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Monetization-Events-1128x696.png 1128w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Monetization-Events-564x348.png 564w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Monetization-Events-375x231.png 375w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Monetization-Events.png 1196w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p class="is-style-body-md">The Monetization category in the Live Events Calendar also lists many more different IAP bundles and offers for players to purchase.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading is-style-title-md">Battle Pass Feature Is a Top Revenue Driver</h2>



<p class="is-style-body-md">In particular, the Battle Pass feature has been crucial for Hero Wars. Battle Pass is a season-based monetization mechanic in which players can obtain rewards by progressing through different thresholds in the plan. They proved particularly effective during the event&#8217;s concluding days, driving revenue spikes as players strived to reap final rewards.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="669" src="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Battle-Pass-Revenue-Spikes-1-1024x669.png" alt="" class="wp-image-35035" srcset="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Battle-Pass-Revenue-Spikes-1-1024x669.png 1024w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Battle-Pass-Revenue-Spikes-1-300x196.png 300w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Battle-Pass-Revenue-Spikes-1-72x47.png 72w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Battle-Pass-Revenue-Spikes-1-900x588.png 900w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Battle-Pass-Revenue-Spikes-1-1128x737.png 1128w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Battle-Pass-Revenue-Spikes-1-564x369.png 564w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Battle-Pass-Revenue-Spikes-1-375x245.png 375w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Battle-Pass-Revenue-Spikes-1.png 1524w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p class="is-style-body-md">The game&#8217;s Battle Pass feature has also evolved through three iterations<strong> </strong>(<a href="https://app.gamerefinery.com/live-events-tracker/games?additionalDatas=gameVersion%2CtopIAPs%2CrevenueChange%2CdownloadChange%2CauChange%2CaverageRevenuePerDailyActiveUser&amp;dateFrom=1745787600000&amp;dateTo=1748465999999&amp;feedDateFrom=1714510800000&amp;feedDateTo=1748379599999&amp;gameIds=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;performanceChangesBy=Peak_1_days&amp;performanceEffectThreshold=0.05&amp;sortGamesBy=SustainedGrossingRank&amp;modalType=liveEvent&amp;m_trackedGameId=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;m_liveEventTypeId=634fad63f651c500a9755fee&amp;m_liveEventId=6548a718f8d2d121fa5e1122&amp;m_tab=Description" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Hero&#8217;s Way</a>, <a href="https://app.gamerefinery.com/live-events-tracker/games?additionalDatas=gameVersion%2CtopIAPs%2CrevenueChange%2CdownloadChange%2CauChange%2CaverageRevenuePerDailyActiveUser&amp;dateFrom=1745787600000&amp;dateTo=1748465999999&amp;feedDateFrom=1714510800000&amp;feedDateTo=1748379599999&amp;gameIds=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;performanceChangesBy=Peak_1_days&amp;performanceEffectThreshold=0.05&amp;sortGamesBy=SustainedGrossingRank&amp;modalType=liveEvent&amp;m_trackedGameId=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;m_liveEventTypeId=634fad63f651c500a9755fee&amp;m_liveEventId=664291bec9c8062e67e3c911&amp;m_tab=Description" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Hero&#8217;s Way 2.0</a> &amp; <a href="https://app.gamerefinery.com/live-events-tracker/games?additionalDatas=gameVersion%2CtopIAPs%2CrevenueChange%2CdownloadChange%2CauChange%2CaverageRevenuePerDailyActiveUser&amp;dateFrom=1745787600000&amp;dateTo=1748465999999&amp;feedDateFrom=1714510800000&amp;feedDateTo=1748379599999&amp;gameIds=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;performanceChangesBy=Peak_1_days&amp;performanceEffectThreshold=0.05&amp;sortGamesBy=SustainedGrossingRank&amp;modalType=liveEvent&amp;m_trackedGameId=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;m_liveEventTypeId=634fad63f651c500a9755fee&amp;m_liveEventId=66fd0a0e67f68602454e8784&amp;m_tab=Description" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Hero&#8217;s Way 3.0</a>), underscoring the critical role of continuous improvement.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="392" src="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Battle-Pass-1024x392.png" alt="" class="wp-image-35036" style="width:1128px;height:auto" srcset="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Battle-Pass-1024x392.png 1024w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Battle-Pass-300x115.png 300w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Battle-Pass-1536x588.png 1536w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Battle-Pass-72x28.png 72w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Battle-Pass-900x345.png 900w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Battle-Pass-1128x432.png 1128w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Battle-Pass-564x216.png 564w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Battle-Pass-375x144.png 375w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Battle-Pass.png 1844w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p class="is-style-body-md">Finally, Hero Wars expanded its Battle Pass offerings in September 2024 by introducing the &#8216;<a href="https://app.gamerefinery.com/live-events-tracker/games?additionalDatas=gameVersion%2CtopIAPs%2CrevenueChange%2CdownloadChange%2CauChange%2CanalystReview%2CaverageRevenuePerDailyActiveUser&amp;dateFrom=1743199200000&amp;dateTo=1748465999999&amp;feedDateFrom=1748293200000&amp;feedDateTo=1748465999999&amp;gameIds=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;liveEventTags=634fad63f651c500a9755fee&amp;performanceChangesBy=Peak_1_days&amp;performanceEffectThreshold=0.05&amp;shotModalIso=us&amp;sortGamesBy=SustainedGrossingRank&amp;modalType=liveEvent&amp;m_trackedGameId=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;m_liveEventTypeId=634fad63f651c500a9755fee&amp;m_liveEventId=66d75e0bcefe4b66c3dbf9ea&amp;m_tab=Description" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Season Pass</a>’ alongside Hero&#8217;s Way 3.0. This &#8216;Season Pass&#8217; repurposes the Hero&#8217;s Way 2.0 framework, doubling the active Battle Pass opportunities.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading is-style-title-md">From Lara Croft to Titan Power: Hero Wars&#8217;s Expanding Event Horizon</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading is-style-title-md">The collaboration with Lara Croft in May 2024</h3>



<p class="is-style-body-md">IP collaborations are increasingly popular within the gaming industry, making thematic cohesion even more crucial. Strategic partnerships with recognizable IPs can help build structured events and streamline content delivery. This, in turn, can lead to significant reductions in player acquisition costs.<br><strong><br></strong>In May 2024, Hero Wars brought its first-ever collaboration event featuring the famous adventurer <a href="https://app.gamerefinery.com/live-events-tracker/games/gameupdate/587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b/1.200.002/us/screenshots/66bc7322dd8bd204a528aff9,66bc7322dd8bd204a528afe6,66bc7322dd8bd204a528afe4?shotModalIso=us" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Lara Croft</a>. This unique crossover created an adventure-themed &#8221;Tomb Raider&#8221; atmosphere.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="649" src="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-IP-Collaboration-Lara-Croft-1024x649.png" alt="" class="wp-image-35037" srcset="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-IP-Collaboration-Lara-Croft-1024x649.png 1024w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-IP-Collaboration-Lara-Croft-300x190.png 300w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-IP-Collaboration-Lara-Croft-1536x974.png 1536w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-IP-Collaboration-Lara-Croft-72x46.png 72w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-IP-Collaboration-Lara-Croft-900x571.png 900w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-IP-Collaboration-Lara-Croft-1128x715.png 1128w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-IP-Collaboration-Lara-Croft-564x358.png 564w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-IP-Collaboration-Lara-Croft-375x238.png 375w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-IP-Collaboration-Lara-Croft.png 1842w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="612" src="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Lara-Croft-1024x612.png" alt="" class="wp-image-35038" srcset="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Lara-Croft-1024x612.png 1024w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Lara-Croft-300x179.png 300w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Lara-Croft-1536x917.png 1536w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Lara-Croft-72x43.png 72w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Lara-Croft-900x537.png 900w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Lara-Croft-1128x674.png 1128w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Lara-Croft-564x337.png 564w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Lara-Croft-375x224.png 375w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Lara-Croft.png 2048w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



