</ul>



<p class="is-style-body-md">In the event, the player must progress in the adventure to gain access to different items. Some levels require the player to play a <a href="https://app.gamerefinery.com/live-events-tracker/games/gameupdate/587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b/1.200.002/us/screenshots/66bc7322dd8bd204a528b010,66bc7322dd8bd204a528b00f,66bc7322dd8bd204a528b00e,66bc7322dd8bd204a528b00d,66bc7322dd8bd204a528b00c,66bc7322dd8bd204a528b00b,66bc7322dd8bd204a528b00a,66bc7322dd8bd204a528b009,66bc7322dd8bd204a528b008,66bc7322dd8bd204a528b007,66bc7322dd8bd204a528b006,66bc7322dd8bd204a528b005,66bc7322dd8bd204a528b004,66bc7322dd8bd204a528b003,66bc7322dd8bd204a528b002,66bc7322dd8bd204a528b001,66bc7322dd8bd204a528b000,66bc7322dd8bd204a528afff?shotModalIso=us">minigame</a> to defeat their enemies, find the exit, and collect rewards from that level. This minigame “style” is also used in user acquisition videos and playables.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="635" src="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lara-Croft-Event-Minigame-1024x635.png" alt="" class="wp-image-35039" style="width:1128px;height:auto" srcset="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lara-Croft-Event-Minigame-1024x635.png 1024w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lara-Croft-Event-Minigame-300x186.png 300w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lara-Croft-Event-Minigame-1536x953.png 1536w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lara-Croft-Event-Minigame-72x45.png 72w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lara-Croft-Event-Minigame-900x558.png 900w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lara-Croft-Event-Minigame-1128x699.png 1128w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lara-Croft-Event-Minigame-564x350.png 564w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lara-Croft-Event-Minigame-375x233.png 375w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lara-Croft-Event-Minigame.png 2048w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="371" src="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lara-Croft-Pre-event-Bundle-Revenue-Spike-1024x371.png" alt="" class="wp-image-35040" srcset="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lara-Croft-Pre-event-Bundle-Revenue-Spike-1024x371.png 1024w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lara-Croft-Pre-event-Bundle-Revenue-Spike-300x109.png 300w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lara-Croft-Pre-event-Bundle-Revenue-Spike-1536x556.png 1536w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lara-Croft-Pre-event-Bundle-Revenue-Spike-72x26.png 72w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lara-Croft-Pre-event-Bundle-Revenue-Spike-900x326.png 900w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lara-Croft-Pre-event-Bundle-Revenue-Spike-1128x409.png 1128w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lara-Croft-Pre-event-Bundle-Revenue-Spike-564x204.png 564w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lara-Croft-Pre-event-Bundle-Revenue-Spike-375x136.png 375w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Lara-Croft-Pre-event-Bundle-Revenue-Spike.png 1684w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p class="is-style-body-md">Players who participate in the Solo Mission event can  also acquire event currency to buy items in the shop. An interesting observation from GameRefinery&#8217;s Live Events calendar was Hero Wars&#8217; introduction of a <a href="https://app.gamerefinery.com/live-events-tracker/games?additionalDatas=gameVersion%2CtopIAPs%2CrevenueChange%2CdownloadChange%2CauChange%2CanalystReview%2CaverageRevenuePerDailyActiveUser&amp;dateFrom=1747083600000&amp;dateTo=1748379599999&amp;feedDateFrom=1748206800000&amp;feedDateTo=1748379599999&amp;gameIds=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;liveEventAppearances=New&amp;performanceChangesBy=Peak_7_days&amp;performanceEffectThreshold=0.05&amp;sortGamesBy=SustainedGrossingRank&amp;modalType=liveEvent&amp;m_trackedGameId=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;m_liveEventTypeId=634ff20cf651c500a9756077&amp;m_liveEventId=663bb6aa6394b66ce047e6d1&amp;m_tab=Description">pre-order bundle for Lara Croft</a> that allowed for early acquisition. This strategic offer culminated caused revenue to surge on its closing day.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading is-style-title-md">Racking up wins with Legends Draft</h3>



<p class="is-style-body-md"><a href="https://app.gamerefinery.com/live-events-tracker/games?additionalDatas=gameVersion%2CtopIAPs%2CrevenueChange%2CdownloadChange%2CauChange%2CaverageRevenuePerDailyActiveUser%2CanalystReview&amp;dateFrom=1747083600000&amp;dateTo=1748379599999&amp;feedDateFrom=1748206800000&amp;feedDateTo=1748379599999&amp;gameIds=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;performanceChangesBy=Peak_7_days&amp;performanceEffectThreshold=0.05&amp;sortGamesBy=SustainedGrossingRank&amp;modalType=liveEvent&amp;m_trackedGameId=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;m_liveEventTypeId=63c549d2d932b600af92a0f7&amp;m_liveEventId=66b2211af9f2b8704583b030&amp;m_tab=Description" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Legends Draft</a> was introduced in August 2024 as an overarching event that boosts the number of events in the game. Played in permanent PVP mode, the event lets the players build teams with a draft mechanic to battle against other players&#8217; teams. Winners rise in the ranking and receive rewards.</p>



<p class="is-style-body-md">In the event, each player chooses a team of five heroes to combat against other players&#8217; teams in fully automated mode. Players need Draft Coins to compete, and these restore up to five coins automatically. You can also use Emeralds (Premium currency) to buy more.</p>



<p class="is-style-body-md">You choose two teams: one for defense and one for offense. The teams will be made with a draft mechanic, where you have three choices of Heroes, and you need to pick one of the three. This will be done five times for each team until both teams have five. You and your opponent choose at the same time a defense team, then an attacking team. Your attacking team will battle against the opponent&#8217;s defense team, and vice versa.<br></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="612" src="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Legends-Event--1024x612.png" alt="Hero Wars Tournament of Titans" class="wp-image-35041" srcset="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Legends-Event--1024x612.png 1024w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Legends-Event--300x179.png 300w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Legends-Event--1536x917.png 1536w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Legends-Event--72x43.png 72w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Legends-Event--900x537.png 900w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Legends-Event--1128x674.png 1128w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Legends-Event--564x337.png 564w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Legends-Event--375x224.png 375w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Legends-Event-.png 2048w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p class="is-style-body-md">Winning your battle will add to your win streak, and you will be rewarded once per day. Each players gets one Win Streak Shield to save their win streak from resetting in the case of a loss—but you can also acquire up to three daily with Emeralds (premium currency). Naturally, the more points from each victory, the higher the streak.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading is-style-title-md">The Tournament of Titan Power!</h3>



<p class="is-style-body-md">Hero Wars has long featured a Tournament of Power, which focuses on leveling up your Heroes. But for the first time in October 2024, players could compete by leveling up their Titans in <a href="https://app.gamerefinery.com/live-events-tracker/feed?additionalDatas=gameVersion%2CtopIAPs%2CrevenueChange%2CdownloadChange%2CauChange%2CaverageRevenuePerDailyActiveUser&amp;dateFrom=1747083600000&amp;dateTo=1748379599999&amp;feedDateFrom=1714510800000&amp;feedDateTo=1748379599999&amp;gameIds=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;liveEventAppearances=New&amp;performanceChangesBy=Peak_7_days&amp;performanceEffectThreshold=0.05&amp;sortGamesBy=SustainedGrossingRank&amp;modalType=liveEvent&amp;m_trackedGameId=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;m_liveEventTypeId=634faf2af651c500a9755ff1&amp;m_liveEventId=66fe95da67f68602454e8b7d&amp;m_tab=Description" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">The Tournament of Titan Power</a>. The first solo tournament focused on Titans, it also contributes to the increase in the number of events on the Hero Wars calendar.<br><br>For newcomers to the game, Titans are another form of characters, such as Heroes, generally obtained through PVE mode by getting shards or from Gachas. Titans differ from the Heroes as they are locked behind Guild mechanics, meaning they are only available if you&#8217;re in a guild, and if you happen to transfer or leave a guild, the Titans remain locked until you join a new guild. Players attempting to access this feature prior to joining a guild are directed to the guild application portal.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large is-resized"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="768" src="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Tournament-of-Titans-1024x768.png" alt="Hero Wars Tournament of Titans" class="wp-image-35042" style="width:1127px;height:auto" srcset="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Tournament-of-Titans-1024x768.png 1024w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Tournament-of-Titans-300x225.png 300w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Tournament-of-Titans-1536x1152.png 1536w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Tournament-of-Titans-72x54.png 72w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Tournament-of-Titans-900x675.png 900w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Tournament-of-Titans-1128x846.png 1128w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Tournament-of-Titans-564x423.png 564w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Tournament-of-Titans-375x281.png 375w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Tournament-of-Titans.png 2048w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p class="is-style-body-md">Getting points in the tournament is simple: you have to upgrade the power levels of your titan characters, and your tournament score equals the power increase of all your titans. There are four different stages with different rewards that unlock when you get enough tournament points. These refresh daily. Rewards include Titian Skin Stones, Titan Potions, and Elemental or Summoning Spheres.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="611" src="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Tournament-of-Titans-3-1024x611.png" alt="Hero Wars Tournament of Titans" class="wp-image-35043" srcset="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Tournament-of-Titans-3-1024x611.png 1024w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Tournament-of-Titans-3-300x179.png 300w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Tournament-of-Titans-3-1536x917.png 1536w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Tournament-of-Titans-3-72x43.png 72w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Tournament-of-Titans-3-900x537.png 900w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Tournament-of-Titans-3-1128x673.png 1128w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Tournament-of-Titans-3-564x337.png 564w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Tournament-of-Titans-3-375x224.png 375w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Tournament-of-Titans-3.png 2048w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p class="is-style-body-md">The main rewards for the winner include Fairy Dust, Titan Potions, and an Avatar. The event lasts 3 to 5 days and recurs at intervals ranging from 19 days to 1.5 months.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading is-style-title-md">New Event Type: Seer&#8217;s Game </h3>



<p class="is-style-body-md">One example of a monetization-related event we discussed is <a href="https://app.gamerefinery.com/live-events-tracker/games?additionalDatas=gameVersion%2CtopIAPs%2CrevenueChange%2CdownloadChange%2CauChange%2CanalystReview%2CaverageRevenuePerDailyActiveUser&amp;dateFrom=1747170000000&amp;dateTo=1748465999999&amp;feedDateFrom=1748293200000&amp;feedDateTo=1748465999999&amp;gameIds=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;performanceChangesBy=Impact_7_days&amp;performanceEffectThreshold=0.1&amp;shotModalIso=us&amp;sortGamesBy=SustainedGrossingRank&amp;modalType=liveEvent&amp;m_trackedGameId=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;m_liveEventTypeId=63510597f651c500a9756098&amp;m_liveEventId=67f1261d32afda78ae2b100e&amp;m_tab=Description"><strong>Seer&#8217;s Game</strong></a>, a Russian roulette-style event introduced in March 2025 as a new event type. In the event, players test their luck to win resources and prizes. They participate by drawing cards, each round offering a chance to win rewards or encounter a cursed card that ends the round.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="613" src="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Seers-Game-1024x613.png" alt="" class="wp-image-35044" srcset="https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Seers-Game-1024x613.png 1024w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Seers-Game-300x180.png 300w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Seers-Game-1536x920.png 1536w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Seers-Game-72x43.png 72w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Seers-Game-900x539.png 900w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Seers-Game-1128x675.png 1128w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Seers-Game-564x338.png 564w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Seers-Game-375x224.png 375w, https://liftoff.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Hero-Wars-Seers-Game.png 2048w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p class="is-style-body-md">To win prizes and advance to the next round, the player must choose a card from two to four options. There are 30 rounds in the game, and each attempt costs 25 Seer&#8217;s Orbs. The orbs can be obtained from <a href="https://app.gamerefinery.com/live-events-tracker/games?additionalDatas=gameVersion%2CtopIAPs%2CrevenueChange%2CdownloadChange%2CauChange%2CanalystReview%2CaverageRevenuePerDailyActiveUser&amp;dateFrom=1747170000000&amp;dateTo=1748465999999&amp;feedDateFrom=1748293200000&amp;feedDateTo=1748465999999&amp;gameIds=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;performanceChangesBy=Peak_1_days&amp;performanceEffectThreshold=0.05&amp;shotModalIso=us&amp;sortGamesBy=SustainedGrossingRank&amp;modalType=liveEvent&amp;m_trackedGameId=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;m_liveEventTypeId=6350fbb7f651c500a9756082&amp;m_liveEventId=67f118f4526fef55f84fabe1&amp;m_tab=Description" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">tasks</a> or <a href="https://app.gamerefinery.com/live-events-tracker/games?additionalDatas=gameVersion%2CtopIAPs%2CrevenueChange%2CdownloadChange%2CauChange%2CanalystReview%2CaverageRevenuePerDailyActiveUser&amp;dateFrom=1747170000000&amp;dateTo=1748465999999&amp;feedDateFrom=1748293200000&amp;feedDateTo=1748465999999&amp;gameIds=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;performanceChangesBy=Peak_1_days&amp;performanceEffectThreshold=0.05&amp;shotModalIso=us&amp;sortGamesBy=SustainedGrossingRank&amp;modalType=liveEvent&amp;m_trackedGameId=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;m_liveEventTypeId=634ff20cf651c500a9756077&amp;m_liveEventId=67f116d4526fef55f84fabde&amp;m_tab=Description" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">bundles</a>. In each round, one card is cursed and will end the round if chosen.&nbsp;Players can continue by using more orbs, and the cost increases with each purchase. Some rounds have no cursed cards, indicated by a special mark. Rewards accumulate as players progress through rounds.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading is-style-title-md">Tower 2.0: revamping a popular event</h3>



<p class="is-style-body-md"><a href="https://app.gamerefinery.com/live-events-tracker/feed?additionalDatas=gameVersion%2CtopIAPs%2CrevenueChange%2CdownloadChange%2CauChange%2CaverageRevenuePerDailyActiveUser&amp;dateFrom=1747083600000&amp;dateTo=1748379599999&amp;feedDateFrom=1714510800000&amp;feedDateTo=1748379599999&amp;gameIds=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;liveEventAppearances=New&amp;performanceChangesBy=Peak_7_days&amp;performanceEffectThreshold=0.05&amp;sortGamesBy=SustainedGrossingRank&amp;modalType=liveEvent&amp;m_trackedGameId=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;m_liveEventTypeId=63c54a4d25b67100af5aa371&amp;m_liveEventId=678d431f9808307c6c29baf9&amp;m_tab=Description" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Tower 2.0</a>, which is a Permanent PVE Mode, was revamped in January 2025. It&#8217;s a daily event where the player aims to get to the top of the tower by defeating enemy teams, collecting buffs, and opening chests.</p>



<p class="is-style-body-md">Let’s talk about the changes to the previous version of <a href="https://app.gamerefinery.com/live-events-tracker/games?additionalDatas=gameVersion%2CtopIAPs%2CrevenueChange%2CdownloadChange%2CauChange%2CanalystReview%2CaverageRevenuePerDailyActiveUser&amp;dateFrom=1747170000000&amp;dateTo=1748465999999&amp;feedDateFrom=1748293200000&amp;feedDateTo=1748465999999&amp;gameIds=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;performanceChangesBy=Peak_1_days&amp;performanceEffectThreshold=0.05&amp;shotModalIso=us&amp;sortGamesBy=SustainedGrossingRank&amp;modalType=liveEvent&amp;m_trackedGameId=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;m_liveEventTypeId=63c54a4d25b67100af5aa371&amp;m_liveEventId=6531311cc7a27e2556b5809f&amp;m_tab=Description">Tower</a>:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Before, there were three level types: one with chests, one with buff altars, and one where the player fights. Now, there are just three types of floors: Relic Floors, Treasure Floors, and a final, Boss Floor. This simplifies the floor types and streamlines the experience.</li>



<li>Before, by winning battles, the player earned Skulls, which can be used to get different buffs at the altar levels. Now, winning battles allows you to choose one out of three Relics. This is a clearer buff and relic system. Relics are chosen after winning battles, making them more immediate.</li>



<li>The energy and health levels of the heroes used to not reset between battles. Now, the energy and health levels of the heroes reset between each Relic Floor. This is a major gameplay change, making each Relic Floor a fresh start for heroes.</li>



<li><em>In the previous version, chests gained from levels contain gold, Tower coins, or random item fragments</em>. Tower 2.0 has &#8220;Treasure Floors&#8221; with three chests. The first is free, and the next two cost &#8220;Emeralds&#8221; (premium currency). One of the chests contains gold, another Tower coins, and the third one contains fragments. This offers a more strategic, potentially more rewarding experience while providing a clear monetization avenue for the game.</li>



<li><em>In Tower, points reward the player with Tower coins and gold at the end of the day. In Tower 2.0, g</em>old is directly earned by winning Battles or Chests.&nbsp;</li>



<li><em>In the previous version, gold from chests increases by 10% after three chests and 40% after 15 chests and with VIP level. </em>Now, you get 25% more gold if your VIP Level is 6. The tiered increase based on the number of chests is removed.<br></li>
</ul>



<p class="is-style-body-md"><strong>Summary</strong><br>Hero Wars has consistently ranked among the top 100 grossing games on US iOS since 2019, <strong>demonstrating remarkable long-term success</strong>. A key factor in its sustained success is the increased number of live events, especially monetization-focused events and staying on top of the latest trends.<br><br>The highlights we covered here were:</p>



<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Lara Croft Collaboration (May 2024): This was the game&#8217;s first collaboration event, featuring a &#8220;Tomb Raider&#8221; themed adventure, solo missions, and various IAP bundles. A pre-order bundle for Lara Croft significantly boosted revenue on its last day.</li>



<li>Legends Draft (August 2024): A permanent PvP mode where players draft teams of heroes to battle others for rankings and rewards, while introducing options to use premium currency. </li>



<li>The Tournament of Titan Power (October 2024): A new solo tournament focusing on leveling up Titans, a separate character type “linked” to guild mechanics.</li>



<li>Seer&#8217;s Game (March 2025): A new monetization event based on a Russian roulette-style card drawing game, offering rewards and requiring &#8220;Seer&#8217;s Orbs&#8221; to participate.</li>



<li>Tower 2.0 Revamp (January 2025): A permanent PvE mode that was significantly revamped, streamlining floor types, altering the relic/buff system, resetting hero health and energy between certain floors, and a direct gold reward from battles.</li>
</ul>



<p class="is-style-body-md">These highlights are just a small fraction of the <a href="https://app.gamerefinery.com/live-events-tracker/games?additionalDatas=gameVersion,topIAPs,revenueChange,downloadChange,auChange,averageRevenuePerDailyActiveUser&amp;dateFrom=1747083600000&amp;dateTo=1748379599999&amp;feedDateFrom=1714510800000&amp;feedDateTo=1748379599999&amp;gameIds=587e85dcbc85fa43c6a8888b&amp;performanceChangesBy=Peak_1_days&amp;performanceEffectThreshold=0.05&amp;sortGamesBy=SustainedGrossingRank" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">game&#8217;s large live event calendar</a>.  We highly recommend taking a look at it, especially the overarching themes!</p>



